        public boolean gaussianArrange​(int row,
                               int column)
        A method to be used if the value at matrix[row][column] is 0, this finds a different line that is acceptable
        Parameters:
        row - The row that is unacceptable, also the row to move the new row to;
        column - The column of the row that cannot be 0
        Returns:
        Whether or not a satisfactory row was found, if false the matrix may be unsolvable
